    <h1>Football Prediction App</h1>
    <h2>PRIVACY POLICY & TERMS OF SERVICE</h2>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> September 2025</p>

    <h2>INFORMATION WE COLLECT</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username and email address for authentication</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> App interactions, prediction views, and feature usage for analytics</li>
        <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, and advertising ID for ad personalization</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide football prediction services and VIP tier access</li>
        <li>Enable community chat features between users</li>
        <li>Process in-app purchases for VIP subscriptions</li>
        <li>Display personalized advertisements through Google AdMob</li>
        <li>Send notifications about new predictions and app updates</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>COMMUNITY FEATURES</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Users can participate in community chat and prediction discussions</li>
        <li>Messages are stored on our servers and visible to other users</li>
        <li>Users must be 18+ to use the app and agree to these terms</li>
        <li>Prohibited content includes adult material, violence, harassment, or illegal activities</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>IN-APP PURCHASES</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>VIP subscriptions provide access to premium predictions with higher accuracy</li>
        <li>Purchases are processed through Google Play Store</li>
        <li>VIP tiers: Basic ($2.99), Standard ($9.99), Premium ($24.99), Ultra VIP ($49.99)</li>
        <li>No refunds for digital content once accessed</li>
        <li>Subscriptions do not auto-renew and are one-time purchases</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>ADVERTISING</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>We display ads through Google AdMob to support the free app</li>
        <li>Ad partners may collect device information for personalized advertising</li>
        <li>Users can watch rewarded ads to unlock free predictions</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>DATA SECURITY</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>All data is encrypted and stored securely using Supabase infrastructure</li>
        <li>We do not share personal information with third parties except ad networks</li>
        <li>Users can delete their account and data through the profile settings</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>DISCLAIMER</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Predictions are for entertainment purposes only</li>
        <li>We do not guarantee prediction accuracy or betting outcomes</li>
        <li>Users are responsible for their own betting decisions</li>
        <li>This app does not facilitate gambling or betting transactions</li>
    </ul>

